name: GDSC IIT Jammu
desc: The Google Developer Student Club (GDSC) at IIT Jammu is a club open to all undergraduate and graduate students with an interest in learning about what it means to be a developer. By joining our chapter, club members learn what it means to form the bridge between the theory and concepts taught in classes and practice with industry developer tools.
